trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDisplayModeEventArgs> class contains information for the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.DisplayModeChanged> event.
trans-unit.target: El <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDisplayModeEventArgs> clase contiene información de la <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.DisplayModeChanged> eventos.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDisplayModeEventArgs> class provides access to the display mode that was applied to the Web Parts control before the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.DisplayModeChanged> event.
trans-unit.target: El <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDisplayModeEventArgs> clase proporciona acceso al modo de presentación que se aplica a lo controles de elementos Web antes de la <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.DisplayModeChanged> eventos.

trans-unit.source: The former display mode is accessed through the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDisplayModeEventArgs.OldDisplayMode%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: El modo de presentación anterior se accede a través del <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDisplayModeEventArgs.OldDisplayMode%2A> propiedad.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDisplayMode" /> applied to the Web Parts control before the display mode is changed.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDisplayMode" /> aplicado al control de elementos Web antes de que se cambie el modo de presentación.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDisplayModeEventArgs" /> class.
trans-unit.target: Inicializa una nueva instancia de la clase <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDisplayModeEventArgs" />.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the former display mode for a Web Part control.
trans-unit.target: Obtiene o establece el modo de presentación anterior para un control de elementos Web

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDisplayMode" /> applied to a Web Parts control before the <see cref="E:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.DisplayModeChanged" /> event.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDisplayMode" /> aplicado a un control de elementos Web antes que el evento <see cref="E:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.DisplayModeChanged" />.
